# No Dead Trees
- Automatically replace all dead trees in your map with a predefined tree state set on settings.

- The script runs every 30 seconds for performance reasons and it can take a while to update all trees.

- You can change the tree state you want your dead trees to update in the mod settings.

- Sometimes, trees show up as dead but when you hover them, they update to the new tree state. A fix for it is to zoom very far away and go to the edge of the map and come back to the same place. Your trees will be updated.
  </LongDescription>
